With the frequency that a warrior/paladin's armor becomes damaged, they<br>
acquire some skill in caring for and repairing them.  Also able to help<br>
the smiths who do the full repairs, the smiths in their kindness, reduce<br>
the cost for repairing the items to full condition.  This is an autoskill.<br>
